DISINTIGRATE

Usage       : cast 'disintigrate' <target>
Accumulative: -
Duration    : instantaneous
Save        : Versus spell for half damage.

   This is the most powerful offensive spell known at this time.  It does
Level(d15) damage to whomever it is cast upon, but requires an intense
devotion to the thaumatergical arts in order to be used at all.  (i.e.
you must be single class)

See also: METEOR SWARM
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
 
